				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A henchman of Gekh Coal, a duergar follower of the Absolute, stops the player when he sees them interacting with a raft that'll let them progress across a lake and beyond his reach. If they haven't yet fulfilled their promise to help him, he warns them to leave the raft alone. "
